title: Viveiro CF
text: Viveiro Club de Fútbol is a <a href="List%20of%20football%20clubs%20in%20Spain">football</a> club based in <a href="Viveiro">Viveiro</a> in the autonomous community of <a href="Galicia%20%28Spain%29">Galicia</a>. Founded in 1923. Viveiro currently plays in <a href="Tercera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20RFEF">Tercera División RFEF – Group 1</a>.
